E-Commerce Recommendation System (Production Rules)

To Identify conditions such as:

Customer purchase history

Browsing behavior

Customer preferences

Spending habits

Product category trends

#production rules for E-Commerce:
RULE 1:
IF customer frequently buys electronics
THEN recommend new smartphone accessories.

RULE 2:
IF customer viewed laptops more than 3 times in a week
THEN offer a laptop discount.

RULE 3:
IF customer purchased baby products
THEN recommend diapers, baby oil, and toys.

RULE 4:
IF cart value > 10,000 AND customer is a premium member
THEN apply free delivery.

RULE 5:
IF customer likes sports items AND viewed football boots
THEN recommend football jerseys.
